Privacy Policy:

The IoT Configurator app prioritizes user privacy and does not collect or store any personal data. 
Its primary function is to serve as a configuration interface for devices, facilitating the direct transmission of data to them. 
It is important to note that the app does not exert control over how configured devices process the transmitted data. 
The app operates with a commitment to maintaining the confidentiality and security of user information, ensuring a secure and private user experience.

Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy.

Marcin Filipiak
privacy@noweenergie.org
